<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Kristina Abramoff is one of the breakout stars on the latest season of The Bachelor. </p>

<p>And the 24-year-old beauty certainly looked eye-catching as she posed in a skimpy pink bralette and matching skirt on Monday.</p>

<p>Taking to Instagram, Kristina flashed the flesh in the racy outfit which ensured she emphasised her toned midriff.</p>

<p>Think Pink! On Monday, The Bachelor's Kristina Abramoff, 24, (pictured) flaunted her toned midriff in a bralette and skimpy skirt in an Instagram photo shoot</p>

<p>The beauty was toned and tanned in the outfit, which clung to her slender figure and also offered a generous glimpse of her cleavage. </p>

<p>Meanwhile, she carried her belongings in a Jacquemus bag. </p>

