<p>Stylish: Taking to Instagram, Kristina flashed the flesh in the racy outfit which ensured she emphasised her toned midriff. She carried her belongings in a Jacquemus bag</p>

<p>On Friday, the 24-year-old offered proof she had completed her Bachelor's degree amid claims she is a paid actress who only went on the show for fame.</p>

<p>Sharing a video to her YouTube account, the brunette answered several burning questions during a 12-minute Q&amp;A session about her experience on the reality series.</p>

<p>'No, I don't have a degree. Absolutely do not have a degree. I just made this up,' she sarcastically told the camera, as she held-up her certificate. </p>

<p>Q&amp;A: Sharing a video to her YouTube account, the brunette answered several burning questions during a 12-minute Q&amp;A session about her experience on the reality series</p>

<p>'Bachelor of Science. Kristina Joey Abramoff, yes, my middle name is Joey,' she added.</p>

<p>'That's my first degree, a Bachelor of Science and Physiology.... and my second is a first class honours in Sports Science, Exercise and Health.'</p>

<p>Kristina then went on to explain that her PhD, which she is currently working towards, is on clinical research and is focused on type one diabetes.  </p>

